<main class="pb-8 sm:pb-12 lg:pb-12">
  <div class="pt-8 overflow-hidden sm:pt-12 lg:relative lg:py-48">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <div>
        <div class="sm:ml-1">
          <%= render "shared/logo", height: "h-11 sm:h-16" %>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-20">
          <div class="mt-6 sm:max-w-xl">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-extrabold text-ts-blue dark:text-slate-200 tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
              Tidy up your Twitter profile in two clicks
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <span class="font-black text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400">Tweet Sweeper</span> automatically deletes your old tweets so you can show off the current you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= render "sign_in_dash_button" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-6">
      <div class="py-12 sm:relative sm:mt-12 sm:py-16 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="hidden sm:block">
          <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-1/2 w-screen bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-l-3xl lg:left-80 lg:right-0 lg:w-full"></div>
          <svg class="absolute top-8 right-1/2 -mr-3 lg:m-0 lg:left-0" width="404" height="392" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 404 392">
            <defs>
            <pattern id="837c3e70-6c3a-44e6-8854-cc48c737b659" x="0" y="0" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="4" height="4" class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-600" fill="currentColor" />
            </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect width="404" height="392" fill="url(#837c3e70-6c3a-44e6-8854-cc48c737b659)" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="relative pl-4 -mr-40 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-0 lg:max-w-none lg:h-full lg:pl-12">
          <%= image_tag "homepage-screenshot", class: "w-full rounded-md shadow-xl ring-1 ring-black ring-opacity-5 lg:h-full lg:w-auto lg:max-w-none" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-24">
    <div class="mt-6 prose prose-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mx-auto">
      <h2><span class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-slate-300">Twitter is a chatroom</span></h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-xl leading-8 dark:text-slate-400">You can reach out and talk with the most interesting people in the world, in real-time. There's nothing like it.</p>
      <p>But we're all human. We learn things, form new opinions, and maybe share just a little too much from time to time. Your Twitter timeline should reflect the smarter, funnier, more current you.</p>
      <p><span class="text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-500 font-bold">Tweet Sweeper</span> puts an expiration date on your tweets and automatically purges Twitter of the things "old you" said.</p>
      <p>To see what this looks like for you, sign in with your Twitter account and test out different durations.</p>
      <p>When you're ready to start sweeping, a subscription plan costs just <strong><span class="dark:text-sky-500">$29/year</span></strong>.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, tweet me <a href="https://twitter.com/pbmarcano"><span class="dark:text-sky-500 underline">@pbmarcano</span></a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
